-- MOVES-Luis Castellanos joins BNY Mellon from BofA Merrill Lynch
-- 
-- Wed Oct 29, 2014 03:12PM EDT
-- None



Oct 29 (Reuters) - BNY Mellon <BK.N>, the world's largest custody bank by assets, said it appointed Luis Castellanos as managing director for business development in BNY Mellon Wealth Management in Florida.

The bank said Castellanos will report to Florida regional President Joe Fernandez.